<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-03 00:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1737 &Cx1f; taf-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-EDIT-OBSERVER-NYT &LR;      05-03 0672
