<HEADLINE>
THE FAT GET FATTER: OVERWEIGHT WAS BAD ENOUGH 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (ART ADV: Graphic is being sent to NYT graphic clients.
Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by calling (888)
603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.)  
 (bl)  
 By SHERYL GAY STOLBERG   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ Bettye Travis is 5 feet 5 and weighs 300 pounds. So
when the National Institutes of Health broadened its definition of
