</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-RUSSIA-OUTLOOK-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) 
 MOSCOW: a beggar.  
<TEXT>
