<P>
   THE-MECHANIC _ ATLANTA _ Wax on; wax off. No, I'm not
auditioning for the next ``Karate Kid'' movie. Recent mild
temperatures provided the perfect opportunity to indulge in one of
those traditional rites of spring _ spring cleaning. (Carter,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED
</P>
<P>
   SHARP-DRIVING _ ATLANTA _ Are you one of those people who has
champagne taste but a beer budget? Do you sometimes need space for
six adults? Would you really like the image that goes with a
premium, upscale brand? You might want to glance in a direction you
might not have considered _ the Buick Century. (Sharp, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) MOVED
</P>
<P>
   ENTERTAINMENT/ARTS
</P>
<P>
   TV-SPORTSNIGHT _ Review. Finale of Sports Night, which has been
renewed for next season. (Jubera, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
12.
</P>
<P>
   NEWSSTAND _ Periodicals on the newsstands this week. (O'Briant,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
