   Block caller ID on your phone, and keep your number unlisted.
Never use electronic toll booths on roads. Never leave your mobile
phone on _ your movements can be traced. Do not use store credit or
discount cards.
</P>
<P>
   If you must use the Internet, encrypt your e-mail, reject all
``cookies'' and never give your real name when registering at web
sites. Better still, use somebody else's computer.
