   The goal of privacy advocates is not extreme. Anyone who took
these precautions would merely be seeking a level of privacy
available to all 20 years ago. And yet such behavior now would seem
obsessive and paranoid indeed.
</P>
<P>
   That is a clue to how fast things have changed. To try to
