column are entitled to a special discounted price on this article.
</P>
<P>
   After more than a half-century of healing, teaching, researching
and writing, Dr. Brazelton is truly an American institution:
Professor Emeritus at Harvard Medical School, which recently named
a chair in his honor. Best-selling author of over two dozen books
on child-rearing. Tireless champion of children and families.
