<HEADLINE>
NORMAN MAILER'S NOT THE ONLY ONE WHO'LL DISPUTE TOP 100 NONFICTION
LIST
</HEADLINE>
 
(EDS: Accompanied by NONFICTION-BOOKLIST-LIST) (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By JEFF GUINN 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
