<P>
   NEW BEETLE-INVASION &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Even for those born after 1979, the last model year
for the original Beetle, the New Beetle fuels an emotional response
to its happy, shiny colors, rounded silhouette and flower-bud vase
on the dash (the flower sometimes twirls when the air conditioner
is on full blast). Even now, about one year after the model was
introduced in March 1998, local dealers say New Beetle buyers still
are waiting from one month to more than a year for delivery,
depending on the options requested. By JESSIE MILLIGAN. Story has
moved in ``l'' lifestyle category. (Accompanied by
BC-NEWBEETLE-BUYER.) &QL; 
