<HEADLINE>
THE FORCE WILL NOT BE WITH ME 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By E.J. MONTINI  
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   PHOENIX - It's not like I didn't go to movies in 1977. If
someone that year had asked me which pictures I'd seen, I'd
probably have said, ``All of them.''
</P>
<P>
   Somehow, though, I missed ``Star Wars.''
</P>
